{"tid":354436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「港獨」網頁遭中國砲轟","createTime":"2017-08-10T12:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T12:59:55.000Z","uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bed669d3929498c652295df0dcc380180a6de346","tid":354436,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"一個在YAHOO免費網站註冊的「我是香港人連線」（<a href=\"http://網址為www.geocities.com/hk_front\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%B2%E5%9D%80%E7%82%BAwww.geocities.com%2Fhk_front&d=EFZLmz7Nm0vHz0x7LOGjWQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=aad373c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">網址為www.geocities.com/hk_front</a>)，因倡導香港獨立運動，昨遭中國半官方的中新社點名批判，網站昨天下午也一度關閉。<br />\n<br />\n訴求不成氣候<br />\n<br />\n中新社昨指出，該網站稱香港特區政府是「傀儡政府」，指責CEPA（內地與香港建立更緊密經貿關係安排）是「加強吮吸香港經濟成果」，還聲稱要「在時機成熟之時成立香港國」，提出「香港國」將實行的政體以及國歌、國旗等代表獨立主權的符號。此外，網頁還成立「香港李登輝之友會」，倡導學習李的思想。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該網站成立於去年十一月，但不久即遭封鎖，隨後靠在各大網站提供的免費網頁中。「港獨」在香港不成氣候，但昨天包括中新社與香港《文匯報》都大張旗鼓點名批判。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/property/20050207/1566995/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Fproperty%2F20050207%2F1566995%2F&d=EFZLmz7Nm0vHz0x7LOGjWQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=39468165\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/property/20050207/1566995/</a>"},{"pid":"b481f18612a10409dd459c1e909f30139dd676e8","tid":354436,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"估唔到12年前已有港獨<br />\n<br />\n先驅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507c8b6c5d86b85308fd2d687b6c741c685c2519","tid":354436,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe7d42448985a8f8ae32cf7f8582b9f08cf3bc32","tid":354436,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"Btw我是香港人連線網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfront.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfront.org&d=EFZLmz7Nm0vHz0x7LOGjWQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=a5cbe39d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfront.org</a>"}]}